## Alternative: Remote Intent Detection Workflow (v1.2+)

For maximum composability, you can reference the intent-detection workflow from the distributed bundle:

```yaml
detect_intent:
  type: reference
  workflow: hiivmind/hiivmind-blueprint-lib@v1.0.0:intent-detection
  context:
    arguments: "${arguments}"
    intent_flags: "${intent_flags}"
    intent_rules: "${intent_rules}"
    fallback_action: "show_main_menu"
  next_node: execute_dynamic_route
```

This eliminates the need to maintain local intent detection nodes in your workflow.yaml.

